HEADWORD: Bougainvillæa
<hw>Bou`gain*vil*l⟦ae⟧`a</hw> <pr>(<?/)</pr>, <pos>prop. n.</pos>
<ety>[Named from <etsep>Bougainville</etsep>, the French
navigator.]</ety> <fld>(Bot.)</fld> <def>A genus of plants of the order
